  <div id="text-content_3f5ee6de-dc24-48f2-96bc-88534489ca92" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Hover over the assignment column header and click the<strong> Options</strong> icon.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="curve_grades" data-step-uuid="0c6e2fbb-5bb2-49a9-a6cb-654c818277ac">
    <h2 id="curve_grades" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Open Posting Policy</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/004/795/786/original/f251b3fa-a4dd-43fb-9606-21b7df5e4ea1.png" srcset="" alt="Open Posting Policy" height="401" width="697">
